data.description: "Discover the epitome of comfortable living in this splendid 4-bedroom and 4 bathrooms , 2 car garage residence nestled within the serene South Plantation community in Pharr, Texas. Boasting nearly 3,000 square feet of meticulously updated living space, this home offers a harmonious blend of modern amenities and timeless charm. Recent renovations include exquisite  new flooring , new roof/shingles, new a/c units , new water heater ensuring years of worry-free living.     Situated in an owner's association community, you'll enjoy access to a well-maintained golf course and a sparkling pool - perfect for leisurely afternoons and weekend relaxation.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule an appointment with your real estate agent today to experience all that this remarkable property has to offer."
